{"tid":2492650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京豐台變壓站發生爆炸大火， 消防員2死1傷","createTime":"2021-04-17T09:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T09:34:16.000Z","uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25f7cfd71305946b2466345f68a0b197e94fdb09","tid":2492650,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"北京豐台變壓站發生爆炸大火， 消防員2死1傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京豐台區大紅門集美家居市場周五（16日）有變壓站起火，當局派消防員救火，惟釀成傷亡。北京市消防總隊周六（17日）凌晨通報，救火期間現場突然發生爆炸，導致2名消防員死亡、1名消防員受傷、變壓站1名員工失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n火警發生於當日中午12時許，起火的變壓站為國軒福威斯光儲充供電有限公司。事發前，該電站正在進行施工調試。大火發生後，當局派出47輛消防車共逾200名消防員趕赴現場救火。直至晚上11時40分，明火才被徹底撲滅，大火燒近12小時，現場仍在進行冷卻降溫處理。"},{"pid":"ab3f6089ca1c86ab7247971a1febb997abcc7f8c","tid":2492650,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2b493ea62fbd8f8a05d303319a5d6f11feece1","tid":2492650,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"有無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ad8c9c342257de296362c5622fc0cff8720ca4","tid":2492650,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd84fea86c4a4c9b87bf97424216fb46053b1fb","tid":2492650,"uid":177168,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgm